what is API gateway?

single entry point for all clients that routes request to backend servicces

we expose only API gateway to the UI, it handled authencitacaion ,
routing and loggin, reducing coupling with backend serrvices

⚠️ Why not call microservices directly from UI?
✅ Answer:
It increases security risk, tight coupling, and makes client changes harder.

2️⃣ Service Discovery Pattern

needed for container restart, ips change dynamically
tool: netflix eureka

each service registers with eureak at startup and resolved other services dynamicaly

do we still need eureka in kubernetes?
no kubenerte provides buit in DNS-Based serrvice discovery

